options.content:
You must enable the ZapiPerf collector in your harvest config and enable smb2.yaml section in your $HARVEST/conf/zapiperf/default.yaml file. 
Please see https://netapp.github.io/harvest/latest/configure-templates/#create-a-new-object-template for more details.
